

#Build markup keyboard

 1. select category using colors
 2. each categ has group of emtion
    categs is identified by color
    e.g
      red => sad, angry
      green => happy

 3. take selected emtion then highlight circle
 4. reply with same keyboard again (back to step 1)
    ask if user wants to add any other emtion on same circle

 *Keyboard should contain done button
 *Keyboard should contain Start over button
 *Inline should be supported

#Circle map

 1. Get pixel coordinates of every emtion
 2. Make a big list with emtion and their coords
 3. Craft small circle filled with same emtion color use as Highlight
 4. Paste crafted circle to emtion coords
 5. Try to preserve jpeg quality 

